headline: Labcorp Holdings (NYSE:LH) Partners With Frame to Enhance Fertility Testing Access
summary: Labcorp Holdings (NYSE:LH) saw a 16% increase in its share price last month, a move that may be linked to its recent partnership with Frame to bolster fertility testing access. This collaboration, announced in May, emphasizes Labcorp's comprehensive capabilities in fertility care—a timely development given the rise in demand for such services. Concurrently, the company reaffirmed its revenue guidance for the year and expanded its precision oncology offerings, which could positively influence...
